{
  "stem": "20684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But so, I did like them and-- and they would water down my vodka because I always have [INAUDIBLE], you know, you get in before you go-- before you go to an expedition that could be your last one and many of them were.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have a few drinks, it doesn't hurt as much to get killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but mine was all watered down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Man, it tasted terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I had to drink.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Big partisan!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] are big boy, so I had to become a fully fledged partisan [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They gave me a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had a good job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They decided after a little while to take me on a-- on a sortie because we were-- we were guarding the hospitals and so.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was different groups of partisans all scattered all over the forest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so I became the feather boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He had a sense of humor, that leader, and he gave me a father and I became known as the feather boy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And what we used to do is they used to ambush German soldiers, German patrols, only in small quantities.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was no shooting, shooting on in self-defense but very rarely that it happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Towards the end of the war, yes, but not-- they-- they-- there-- although they carried guns, there-- there are ways to ambush them, bayonet and hold them up and cut the neck, just slice it from-- from ear to ear.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it takes only two or three seconds to die or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they dropped them dead, but sometimes they didn't do such a good job.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was the feather boy, so they gave me a feather and when the soldiers dropped, I used to put the feather under the nose and count up to 100.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
